# Week_04

## Contents
This folder contains the official weekly reports, career readiness assets, and documentation completed during Week 04 of the CyberProAI Summer 2026 Internship.

## Deliverables
* [**README.md**](./README.md): This configuration file outlining Week 04 milestones, skills gains, and project assets.
* [**Week_04_Work_Report.pdf**](./Week_04_Work_Report.pdf): Formal weekly progress report containing the Bottom Line Up Front (BLUF), internship activities summary, core technical milestone ledger, and a comprehensive project execution progress snapshot.
* [**Week_04_Resume.pdf**](./Week_04_Resume.pdf): Professionally tailored, ATS-friendly cybersecurity resume customized to align with enterprise infrastructure management and vulnerability management requirements, incorporating hands-on cyber range results and system troubleshooting metrics.

## Technical Skills & Portfolio Progression
* **Systems Administration & Triage**: Integrating hands-on troubleshooting metrics from completed range environments, including manual wrapper bypasses and local file permission restrictions.
* **Vulnerability Management Customization**: Aligning core portfolio experience to map directly to enterprise technical competencies (GPOs, software package creations, and deployment automation).
* **Technical Portfolio Architecture**: Organizing professional documentation, reports, and assignments into structural GitHub repository directories suitable for corporate recruiter review.
